<item>
            <title>[HBASE-14900] Make global config option for ReplicationEndpoint</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14900</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently ReplicationEndpoint implementations can only be configured through the HBase shell. We should be able to to use a property in the hbase-site.xml to globally set an alternate default. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
