                            <comment id="15064342" author="apurtell" created="Fri, 18 Dec 2015 17:59:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch lgtm but is missing a unit test. Consider &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=enis&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;enis&quot;&gt;Enis Soztutar&lt;/a&gt; &apos;s suggestion. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15064426" author="ashish singhi" created="Fri, 18 Dec 2015 18:31:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Suggestions:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Can we include configured ReplicationEndpoint in the log when it throws error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Instead of Configuration#get may we can use Configuration#getClass(String, Class&amp;lt;? extends U&amp;gt;, Class&amp;lt;U&amp;gt;) api.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
replicationEndpointImpl = conf.get(HConstants.REPLICATION_ENDPOINT_IMPL,
465	            HBaseInterClusterReplicationEndpoint.class.getName());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
